	<h2><img width="892" height="245" style="vertical-align: text-top; margin: 5px;" src="/sites/default/files/outdoor%20banner.jpg" /></h2>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: medium;">&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-no-proof: yes;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: medium;"><img width="720" height="161" src="data:image/png;base64," v:shapes="Picture_x0020_1" /></span></span></p>
<p></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="color: #595959; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Georgia',serif; font-size: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themetint: 166;">Founded in 2006 by filmmakers Josh Lowell (Big UP Productions) and Peter Mortimer (Sender Films), the REEL ROCK Film Tour brings the best climbing and adventure films of the year to live audiences throughout the world. The film tour is the definitive annual event for climbing communities globally. REEL ROCK shows are high energy, community events that go beyond mere film screenings to include prize giveaways, non-profit fundraising, and a party atmosphere. </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="color: #595959; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Georgia',serif; font-size: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themetint: 166;"><br />In its landmark 10th year, REEL ROCK is kicking off the 2015 world tour to over 450 locations around the world. From big walls to big moves, REEL ROCK 10 features athletes Tommy Caldwell, Kevin Jorgeson, Alex Honnold, Jimmy Webb, Daniel Woods and a special tribute to the late Dean Potter. This year's tour boasts an eclectic program that will get you psyched!</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="color: #595959; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Georgia',serif; font-size: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themetint: 166;"><br />This year Outdoor Pursuits will be hosting REEL ROCK 10 open to students, faculty, staff, and community members. All proceeds will benefit a new stewardship program that will promote river cleanups in the metroplex. By purchasing your $12 ticket, you will automatically be put in a drawing for raffle prizes at the end of the show. Come join us for this exciting screening, enjoy some complimentary popcorn, and meet some new friends!</span></p>
<h2 style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"></h2>
<h2 style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mXNOTJFEBsQ" target="_blank"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>** CHECK OUT THE OFFICIAL TRAILER ON YOUTUBE HERE!**</strong></span></a></h2>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: #595959; line-height: 150%; font-size: 20pt; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themetint: 166;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">REEL ROCK FILM TOUR – Saturday, October 24, 2015 at 5pm</span></span></b></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="color: #595959; line-height: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 20.0pt; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themetint: 166;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: medium;">Tickets: $12</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="color: #595959; line-height: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 20.0pt; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themetint: 166;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: medium;">Location: Pohl Rec Center – Rooms 205/207</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"></p>
<h2 style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong>** <a href="https://recsports.unt.edu/reelrock-tickets%20" target="_blank">PURCHASE YOUR TICKETS HERE!</a> **</strong></h2>
